<li>name (string 200)</li>
<li>description (text, nullable)</li>
<li>type (string: percentage, fixed_amount, buy_x_get_y)</li>
<li>scope (string: order, item)</li>
<li>value (decimal)</li>
<li>max_discount (decimal, nullable)</li>
<li>min_purchase (decimal, nullable)</li>
<li>min_qty (int, nullable)</li>
