<li>membership_levels (json, nullable)</li>
<li>applicable_outlets (json, nullable)</li>
<li>applicable_items (json, nullable)</li>
<li>valid_from (date, nullable)</li>
<li>valid_until (date, nullable)</li>
<li>usage_limit (int, nullable)</li>
<li>usage_count (int)</li>
<li>is_auto_apply (boolean)</li>
<li>is_active (boolean)</li>
<li>created_at, updated_at</li>
</ul>

